data.description: Beautiful home located in the highly sought after Celery Creek area of Sanford Florida. This home has been well cared for. The interesting architecture inside as well as the arch doorways makes this home have a unique warm inviting homey yet classy atmosphere. This home was built in 2004. It has 3 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths. The home is 2021 ft.² atmosphere is everything! No backyard nosy neighbors. Imagine yourself enjoying a hot cup of coffee on the back patio as you watch the birds dive in and out of the water. Your own piece of paradise. Priced to sell quickly.
